titleNullable: Road accidents in Israel by areas
descriptionNullable:
About Dataset: 
This data has been taken from an Israeli government website and contains data on road accidents by region in Israel in the last five years (2017-
2021).
Link for the website: https://data.gov.il/dataset/accid_taz/resource/57c5aef9-70f9-4b71-82fa-52304cfbd031
it contains:
• how many dead and injured?
• Which vehicle is most involved in traffic accidents?
• In which city do the most accidents happen?
• In which traffic areas do the most accidents happen?
 Some of the data is in Hebrew, and part of the columns are written with code names.
I am attaching a link with the explanation of the column names:
https://data.gov.il/dataset/accid_taz/resource/b25db13f-07e6-4ec6-be71-a95bb1b15816
